1524	
1525	  // ─── User Management ──────────────────────────────────────────────
1526	
1527	  /**
1528	   * Register a new user.
1529	   *
1530	   * Bootstrap mechanism — does NOT require authentication.
1531	   * Generates a unique token (`tk_` + 8 random alphanumeric chars) for the user.
1532	   * Names are stored lowercase. The name "anonymous" is reserved.
1533	   *
1534	   * @param name - The user name to register (stored lowercase)
1535	   * @returns `{ result: "OK", name, token }` on success, or `{ result: "USER_ALREADY_EXISTS", message }`
1536	   * @throws {TrackgenticError} NOT_INITIALIZED if no `.trackgentic/` directory
1537	   *
